Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.04,0:00:01.51,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,MENARA MIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.28,0:01:28.77,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,MY HERO ACADEMIA: VIGILANTES SEASON 2
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.36,0:02:43.89,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,DEUS EX MACHINA: ISTILAH TEATER YUNANI\NBERARTI "DEWA DARI MESIN".
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.91,0:02:46.09,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,KINI BERMAKNA PENYELESAIAN\NCERITA YANG DIPAKSAKAN.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.12,0:02:48.37,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,EP.25 INILAH PAHLAWAN
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.86,0:02:58.24,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,"YAGI"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.36,0:05:32.01,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,SMASH!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.30,0:11:07.10,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,NEBRASKA
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.10,0:11:08.52,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,SMASH!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.54,0:00:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selanjutnya, mengenai arah kebijakan\Naktivitas All Might ke depan...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.07,0:00:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pertama, silakan lihat materi\Ndi folder bersama.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.63,0:00:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.24,0:00:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.66,0:00:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mohon aktifkan mode senyap\Nsaat rapat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.86,0:00:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.22,0:00:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saya ke toilet sebentar.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.60,0:00:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.76,0:00:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa, Tsukauchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.03,0:00:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biasanya kau mengirim surel...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.39,0:00:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}All Might! Ada keadaan darurat\Ndi Tokyo Sky Egg!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.23,0:00:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tsukauchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.68,0:00:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sky Egg-nya!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.52,0:00:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akan runtuh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.60,0:01:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, ya. Ini sudah menjadi\Nkatastrofe yang tak terhindarkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.40,0:01:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Takdir tidak bisa diubah\Noleh siapa pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.70,0:01:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kecuali kalau itu Tuhan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.37,0:02:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.86,0:02:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tsukauchi, suara apa tadi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.24,0:03:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bilang Sky Egg?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.43,0:03:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nao!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.06,0:03:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat datang!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.16,0:03:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pulangnya tidak mampir\Nke mana-mana, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.80,0:03:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.66,0:03:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu sungguhan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.50,0:03:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makoto baru saja ke rumah sakit\Nbersama Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.46,0:03:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nao mengkhawatirkan Mako?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.39,0:03:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.64,0:03:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu bohong!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.16,0:03:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bu, bagaimana hasil pemeriksaannya?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.86,0:03:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Katanya itu Quirk yang bisa\Nmembaca hati orang.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.16,0:03:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, seperti dugaanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.80,0:03:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kukira dia hanya anak\Nyang sangat peka.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.80,0:03:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mako menyukai Nao.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.37,0:03:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi apakah Nao menyukai Mako?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.46,0:03:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mako, tidak baik menanyakan\Nhal seperti itu pada orang lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.83,0:04:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak apa-apa,\Nhal seperti itu lucu, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.84,0:04:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak baik jika menjadi kebiasaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.06,0:04:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mengorek perasaan orang\Nbukanlah hal yang benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.36,0:04:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nao memang serius sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.60,0:04:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jawab yang benar!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.26,0:04:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apakah Nao menyukai Mako?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.10,0:04:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah kukatakan,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.95,0:04:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}anak yang berkata begitu...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.74,0:04:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}justru tidak kusukai.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.70,0:04:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebagai seorang polisi,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.70,0:04:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mungkin aku tak seharusnya\Nmengatakan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.30,0:04:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi meski begitu, aku mohon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.30,0:04:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak suka?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.46,0:04:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu bohong!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.63,0:04:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.89,0:04:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong selamatkan adikku!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.89,0:04:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}All Might!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.32,0:04:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.10,0:05:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik, aku akan segera ke sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.80,0:05:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku tak bisa berkata begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.32,0:05:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.03,0:05:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dalam situasi seperti ini,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.50,0:05:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}hanya ada satu kalimat\Nyang harus kuucapkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.54,0:05:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dan kalimat itu adalah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.06,0:05:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.96,0:05:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}All Might!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.03,0:05:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ada di sini!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.86,0:05:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}All Might!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.06,0:05:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}All Might, sendirian saja...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.87,0:06:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mampu menurunkan Sky Egg\Nke tanah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.23,0:06:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Keren sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.16,0:06:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak masuk akal!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.46,0:06:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}All Might! All Might! All Might!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.23,0:06:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}All Might! All Might! All Might!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.76,0:06:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia... menyelamatkan semuanya?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.50,0:06:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}All Might! All Might! All Might!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.90,0:06:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A... All Might...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.90,0:06:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suara ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.23,0:06:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}All Might?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.61,0:06:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya! All Might yang menyelamatkan kita!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.16,0:06:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Syukurlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.56,0:06:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seperti biasa, kau bertindak nekat,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.40,0:06:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}pahlawan nomor satu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.56,0:06:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itukah All Might...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.97,0:06:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pahlawan nomor satu Jepang...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.01,0:06:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}All Might! Ke sini, ke sini!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.65,0:07:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hai, salam kenal,\NCaptain Celebrity!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.16,0:07:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Senang bertemu denganmu,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.03,0:07:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan kerja bagus!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.46,0:07:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong, kau siapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.16,0:07:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hanya seorang penggemar!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.80,0:07:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Boleh meminta tanda tangan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.56,0:07:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}All Might,\Nberikan komentar singkat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.21,0:07:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik, yang terpenting\Ntidak ada korban jiwa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.13,0:07:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, masih banyak orang terluka\Ndan diliputi kecemasan di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.43,0:07:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, tidak, tidak.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat ini juga, pahlawan profesional\Ndan organisasi resmi
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.20,0:07:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sedang bekerja sama untuk mengungkap\Ndan menyelesaikan insiden ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.01,0:07:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin kalian mendukung\Nsemua pahlawan itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.00,0:07:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa-apaan itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.06,0:07:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang sudah aman!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.76,0:07:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Silakan berevakuasi dengan tenang!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.20,0:07:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yah, sepertinya aku gagal\Nmenjadi pahlawan, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.37,0:07:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh? Tidak juga kok, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.83,0:07:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Daripada itu, lihat tanda tangan\NAll Might ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.21,0:08:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, sikapmu sangat berbeda\Ndibanding saat aku yang memberikannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.06,0:08:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang haus, mau teh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.60,0:08:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada juga manju C.C.!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.34,0:08:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini tehnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.76,0:08:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Silakan.\N- Itu adikmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.90,0:08:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Syukurlah dia selamat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.23,0:08:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong soal adik...\NMaaf, tadi aku kehilangan kendali.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.06,0:08:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.70,0:08:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Justru berkat panggilanmu\Nyang penuh perasaan,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.76,0:08:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku bisa datang tepat waktu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.20,0:08:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benarkah begitu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.60,0:08:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kekuatan seseorang bisa membesar\Ntergantung kondisi mentalnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.20,0:08:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dulu kau bilang harus memisahkan\Nurusan pribadi dan pekerjaan, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.65,0:08:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi mendengarkan jeritan orang\Nyang meminta pertolongan
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.25,0:08:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}juga tugas seorang pahlawan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.56,0:08:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku menerima kekuatan ini agar\Nsemua orang bisa memiliki harapan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.47,0:08:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bahwa suara mereka pasti sampai\Nkepada All Might.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.66,0:08:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menerima kekuatan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.52,0:09:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, bukan apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.70,0:09:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, mari kita bantu\Nproses pemulihan, Tsukauchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.44,0:09:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh? Ya...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.46,0:09:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suatu hari nanti,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.00,0:09:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}akan kuceritakan semuanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.90,0:09:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rahasia All Might.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.70,0:09:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa-apaan ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.62,0:09:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa suasananya seperti kelelahan\Nsepulang kerja begitu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.62,0:09:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Padahal tadi aku sudah menahan diri, lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.88,0:09:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan meremehkanku, hei.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.03,0:09:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begini, mau tidak mau\Nakan kubunuh kalian semua.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.30,0:09:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagian tubuh penjahat bom yang meledak tadi
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.80,0:09:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}akan kuregenerasi, kugabungkan,\Ndan kugandakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.07,0:09:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah? Apa itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.00,0:09:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan-jangan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.12,0:09:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebesar monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.56,0:10:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Penjahat bom raksasa?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.76,0:10:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan sekadar besar, lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.41,0:10:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bom mencolok seperti itu pasti akan\Ndinonaktifkan oleh Eraser Head,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.43,0:10:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}atau dihancurkan All Might\Nsebelum meledak.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.86,0:10:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi yang ini spesial.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.13,0:10:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namanya Cluster Bomber.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia bisa melepaskan 200 bom mini\Nsekaligus dari dalam perutnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.43,0:10:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangankan All Might sendirian,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.16,0:10:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bahkan jika semua pahlawan di sini\Nbekerja sama pun,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.86,0:10:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mereka tak akan bisa\Nmengalahkan setengahnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.10,0:10:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau masih tersisa 100,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.03,0:10:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}penonton yang susah payah diselamatkan,\Npolisi, pemadam, ambulans,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.57,0:10:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sekalian juga warga sekitar
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.03,0:10:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bisa musnah semua dengan mudah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.00,0:10:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekelompok... penjahat bom!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.06,0:10:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terlalu banyak! Gawat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.56,0:10:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak mungkin!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.62,0:11:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Dengan satu pukulan saja...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.00,0:11:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Puting beliungnya menarik semua bom mini\Ndan meledakkannya sekaligus!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.63,0:11:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gila sekali!\NApa-apaan itu? Tidak masuk akal!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.10,0:11:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mana ada orang seaneh itu\Ndi dunia ini?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.60,0:11:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar. Nomor 6.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.46,0:11:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pemandangan yang sulit dipercaya,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.89,0:11:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi itu adalah kenyataan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.89,0:11:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Manusia super sejati
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.76,0:11:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}di dimensi berbeda dari pahlawan lainnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.63,0:12:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sosok deus ex machina yang mampu\Nmembengkokkan hukum fisika dan takdir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.58,0:12:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dialah All Might.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.16,0:12:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Puncak yang harus kau capai.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.86,0:12:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Puncak yang harus dicapai, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.00,0:12:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku tidak ingin menjadi All Might.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.46,0:12:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, benar juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.50,0:12:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lakukan saja sesukamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.23,0:12:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.36,0:12:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tujuan Factory adalah
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.03,0:12:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}eksperimen peningkatan Quirk melalui\Nmodifikasi tubuh dan obat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.20,0:12:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Acara berkumpulnya pahlawan top ini\Npasti dijadikan tempat eksperimen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.36,0:12:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bangunan untuk mengamati Sky Egg\Nsudah ditentukan sebelumnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.83,0:12:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jarak 250 meter,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.00,0:12:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}arah angin barat daya 8 m/s.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.10,0:12:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Targetnya kepala.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.06,0:13:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada sesuatu yang melintas\Ndi jalur tembakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.46,0:13:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Burung?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.66,0:13:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berkat itu, tembakan di kepala meleset,\Ntapi pergerakannya berhenti.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.98,0:13:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Halo, selamat siang.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.20,0:13:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cepat sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.80,0:13:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selain Quirk akselerasi,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.86,0:13:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tubuhmu tampaknya sudah\Ndimodifikasi cukup jauh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.76,0:13:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, begitulah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.03,0:13:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sedang meningkatkan otot\Ndan mematikan rasa sakit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.00,0:13:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untuk akselerasi, ini adalah Overclock\Nmilik pahlawan super cepat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.34,0:13:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Quirk milik O'Clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.22,0:13:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah lama\Ningin bertemu denganmu, Guru.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.50,0:13:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga sudah lama mencarimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.76,0:13:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa kau sebenarnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.83,0:13:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pria dengan luka di wajah\Nyang mengendalikan penjahat modifikasi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.90,0:14:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Identitas, riwayat, bahkan namanya\Ntidak diketahui.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.06,0:14:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang pasti hanya satu,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.63,0:14:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kau memiliki Quirk Overclock\Nyang dicuri dariku.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.23,0:14:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Banyak yang ingin kutanyakan,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.50,0:14:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi untuk sekarang,\Nkita mulai dari namamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.56,0:14:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh, nama? Namaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.22,0:14:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah, tertarik kepadaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.03,0:14:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suatu kehormatan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.90,0:14:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku ini belum menjadi siapa-siapa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.03,0:14:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibarat makhluk kecil aneh\Ntanpa bentuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.20,0:14:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka memanggilku subjek uji\Nnomor 6... atau Number Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.56,0:14:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi itu hanya nomor, bukan nama.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.83,0:14:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau suatu saat\Naku bisa menjadi sesuatu,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.63,0:14:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}menjadi seseorang...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.46,0:14:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maka itu adalah O'Clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.20,0:14:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu satu-satunya nama\Nyang akan kugunakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.06,0:14:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau bisa menjadi sesuatu,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.40,0:14:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}menjadi seseorang...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.08,0:14:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang-orang biasanya ingin\Nmenjadi All Might.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.75,0:15:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}All Might, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.90,0:15:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia memang luar biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.23,0:15:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi entah kenapa terasa membatasi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.63,0:15:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena dia hanya mengalahkan penjahat\Ndan menyelamatkan dari bencana.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.20,0:15:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selalu membereskan\Nmasalah orang lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.80,0:15:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Justru itulah pahlawan nomor satu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.26,0:15:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Fakta dia tidak menggunakan kekuatannya\Nuntuk kepentingan pribadi
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.06,0:15:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}adalah keberuntungan\Nbagi seluruh umat manusia.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.46,0:15:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebaliknya, jika kekuatan sebesar itu\Ndigunakan sesuka hati,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.36,0:15:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}maka dunia akan hancur.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.00,0:15:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.53,0:15:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Intinya, kekuatan All Might\Nitu terlalu besar.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.49,0:15:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hanya untuk melindungi dunia\Natau malah menghancurkannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.90,0:15:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak ada pilihan lain.\NTidak bisa digunakan sesuka hati.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.25,0:15:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi bagiku, itu tidak ada artinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.21,0:15:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena aku ingin hidup bebas\Ndengan caraku sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.83,0:15:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak tertarik menolong orang?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.39,0:15:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan tidak sama sekali,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.90,0:15:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi aku akan malas\Njika tidak sepadan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.90,0:16:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makanya aku ingin\Nmenjadi sepertimu, Guru.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.44,0:16:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak butuh kekuatan untuk\Nmenghancurkan gedung.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.03,0:16:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang penting Quirk itu bisa mengambil\Ninisiatif lebih dulu dari siapa pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.94,0:16:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memaksakan alur sendiri kepada lawan\Ndan menang sendirian!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.12,0:16:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itulah O'Clock! Pahlawanku!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.80,0:16:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Membuatku merinding!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.86,0:16:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang seperti itu bukan pahlawan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.20,0:16:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, merendah lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.71,0:16:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku penggemar beratmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.40,0:16:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tahu segalanya tentangmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.40,0:16:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku rela melakukan apa pun\Ndemi menjadi sepertimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.97,0:16:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat aku melihat akhirmu,\Ntubuhku sampai gemetar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.90,0:16:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selanjutnya aku...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.26,0:16:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Giliranku telah tiba...\Nbegitulah pikirku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.56,0:16:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, ini permintaanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.00,0:16:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong akui aku sebagai penerusmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.16,0:16:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekalian saja, aku ingin resmi menyebut\Ndiriku O'Clock generasi kedua.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.66,0:17:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, tapi aku sudah memiliki murid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.03,0:17:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, iya, iya, Koichi, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.90,0:17:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi bagaimanapun juga, aku jauh lebih\Nmenghormati Guru dibanding dia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.01,0:17:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, dia penggemar All Might,\Nbukan penggemarmu, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.64,0:17:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Justru itu alasannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.93,0:17:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah kukatakan,\NO'Clock itu bukan pahlawan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.46,0:17:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika orang yang ingin meniru O'Clock\Nbenar-benar mendapatkan Quirk-nya,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.46,0:17:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}maka dia tak lebih\Ndari penjahat terburuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.26,0:17:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Harus disingkirkan sebagai ancaman\Nbagi masyarakat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.43,0:17:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, begitu.\NJadi, langsung dicap penjahat, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.91,0:17:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, ya sudah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.30,0:17:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, mau bagaimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.38,0:17:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mau menembakku dengan pistol itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.83,0:17:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tadi saja tembakan jarak jauhmu\Ngagal, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.63,0:17:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Atau kau mau bilang dari jarak ini\Ntidak akan meleset?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.42,0:17:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Coba saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.03,0:18:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meleset lagi, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.93,0:18:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku memang sangat menghormatimu,\Nmantan O'Clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.39,0:18:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi tanpa Quirk,\Nkau hanyalah manusia biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.60,0:18:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu aku masuk mode akselerasi,\Nkau tak bisa menghentikanku lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.11,0:18:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat tinggal, Guru.\NJika kau tiada, maka akulah O’Clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.49,0:18:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bisakah kau mendengar pesan ini,\NOverclock...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.20,0:18:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suara apa itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.23,0:18:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rekaman suara...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.64,0:18:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meskipun kau memiliki Quirk
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.87,0:18:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Diputar dengan kecepatan tinggi...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.62,0:18:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}milik pahlawan super cepat O’Clock,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.76,0:18:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kau belum sepenuhnya\Nmemahami sifatnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.70,0:18:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hakikat Quirk Overclock adalah\Naktivasi fungsi otak.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.20,0:18:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini mempercepat persepsi dan pikiran,\Nsehingga waktu terasa melambat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.23,0:18:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tingkat akselerasi ini tidak tetap\Ndan berubah tergantung kondisi mental.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.23,0:18:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat serangan aktif, akselerasinya\Nsekitar dua hingga sepuluh kali lipat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.06,0:18:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat darurat,\Nbisa mencapai puluhan kali lipat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.28,0:19:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika konsentrasi\Nditingkatkan lebih jauh,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.49,0:19:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kau bahkan merasa seolah lingkungan\Nsekitarmu benar-benar berhenti.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.74,0:19:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, akselerasi tingkat tinggi\Nmemiliki batas waktu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.80,0:19:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Otak akan kelelahan\Njika digunakan terlalu intens.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.66,0:19:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makin tinggi akselerasinya,\Nmakin besar konsumsi energi otak.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.17,0:19:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Misalnya, saat menghindari\Npeluru senapan
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.05,0:19:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}atau saat mencoba memahami pesan\Nyang diputar 300 kali lebih cepat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.44,0:19:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sial!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.81,0:19:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Quirk-ku!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.02,0:19:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya sudah terjadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.98,0:19:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kelelahan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.40,0:19:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sayang sekali, tapi tidak ada waktu\Nuntuk menarik napas.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.76,0:19:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ledakan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.76,0:19:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak bisa bergerak di udara!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.86,0:19:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku meledakkan lantai\Nsetinggi tiga tingkat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.20,0:19:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini adalah jatuh bebas\Nuntuk menyegel akselerasi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.60,0:19:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shotgun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.26,0:19:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lindungi kepalamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.70,0:19:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu bagian paling vital.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.86,0:19:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi untuk mendarat, kau butuh kaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.13,0:20:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sudah mengutak-atik\Nrasa sakitmu, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.06,0:20:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, aku harus melumpuhkan\Nfungsi anggota tubuhmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.80,0:20:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aneh sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.77,0:20:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tadi mengincar kepala,\Nsekarang berubah jadi menangkap hidup-hidup?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.40,0:20:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak konsisten, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.80,0:20:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini soal prioritas.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.10,0:20:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dari jarak jauh, yang terbaik adalah\Nmenghabisi dalam satu serangan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.60,0:20:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi jika target masuk\Nke dalam kandang,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.63,0:20:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}maka penangkapan bisa dilakukan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.88,0:20:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebagai tambahan, ledakan berikutnya\Nakan meruntuhkan gedung ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.56,0:20:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bahkan dalam mode akselerasi pun,\Nkau tak akan bisa kabur.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.86,0:20:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kandang ini akan menjadi petimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.64,0:20:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini sudah sekakmat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.86,0:20:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, kau ingin aku mengakui kekalahan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.30,0:20:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Atau sebisa mungkin\Nkau tak ingin membunuhku?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.46,0:20:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selagi kau berbicara manis begitu...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.50,0:20:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lihat, aku sudah selesai mengambil napas.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.19,0:21:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Melenyapkan penjahat berbahaya\Nadalah prioritas utama,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.83,0:21:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi mendapatkan informasi dalangnya\Nitu jauh lebih baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.78,0:21:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cara menahan Overclock termasuk\Nmembuat gegar otak lewat pukulan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.56,0:21:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Artinya, selama dipukul,\Nkau tidak bisa berakselerasi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.10,0:21:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setelah cukup dipukul, aku akan\Nmengikatmu dan menginterogasimu...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.80,0:21:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau juga meningkatkan kemampuan\Npenyembuhanmu, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.10,0:21:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pendarahan di bagian yang terkena\Ntembakan sudah berhenti.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.22,0:21:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Merepotkan juga,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.43,0:21:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi kalau sudah terikat,\Nhasilnya sama saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.00,0:21:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sayang sekali, Guru.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.02,0:21:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di sini, seharusnya kau langsung\Nmenembus kepalaku tanpa ragu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.44,0:21:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengan menanamkan sel\Ndari penjahat bom...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.30,0:21:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bisa mengubah lenganku\Nmenjadi bom.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.98,0:23:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setelah berbagai insiden terselesaikan,\NCaptain kembali ke Amerika.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.01,0:23:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dua tahun kemudian,\Naku membuat sebuah keputusan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.66,0:23:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selanjutnya,\N"Kelulusan dan Jenjang Karier".
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.86,0:23:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Haimawari Koichi, The Crawler,\Nakan lulus!
